---
---

<section id="services" class="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag" data-i18n="svc.tag">What We Install</span>
      <h2 data-i18n="svc.h2">Complete Fence Installation Services<br /><span class="highlight">in Montreal &amp; Laval</span></h2>
      <p data-i18n="svc.p">From wood privacy fences to code-compliant pool barriers, we handle every fence type for residential and commercial properties across Greater Montreal.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#127795;</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="w.h3">Wood Fence<br /><small>Clôture en Bois</small></h3>
        <p data-i18n="w.p">Classic cedar and pressure-treated wood fences for maximum privacy and curb appeal. Custom heights and styles to match your Montreal or Laval property perfectly.</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="w.li1">Privacy &amp; picket fences</li>
          <li data-i18n="w.li2">Cedar, pine &amp; treated wood</li>
          <li data-i18n="w.li3">Custom heights up to 8 ft</li>
          <li data-i18n="w.li4">Staining &amp; finishing available</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link" data-i18n="svc.link">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card featured">
        <div class="service-badge-top" data-i18n="pool.badge">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="service-icon">&#128737;</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="pool.h3">Pool Fence<br /><small>Clôture de Piscine</small></h3>
        <p data-i18n="pool.p">Code-compliant pool fencing that meets all Quebec and municipal safety requirements. Protect your family and increase your property value with a beautiful pool enclosure.</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="pool.li1">Meets RBQ safety codes</li>
          <li data-i18n="pool.li2">Aluminum &amp; tempered glass options</li>
          <li data-i18n="pool.li3">Self-closing / self-latching gates</li>
          <li data-i18n="pool.li4">In-ground &amp; above-ground pools</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link" data-i18n="svc.link">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#127968;</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="vinyl.h3">Vinyl Fence<br /><small>Clôture en Vinyle</small></h3>
        <p data-i18n="vinyl.p">Low-maintenance PVC and vinyl fences that never rot, warp or need painting. Perfect for Montreal's harsh winters and hot summers — beautiful year after year.</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="vinyl.li1">Zero maintenance required</li>
          <li data-i18n="vinyl.li2">Weather &amp; frost resistant</li>
          <li data-i18n="vinyl.li3">Wide range of colors &amp; styles</li>
          <li data-i18n="vinyl.li4">25-year manufacturer warranty</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link" data-i18n="svc.link">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#9711;</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="alum.h3">Aluminum Fence<br /><small>Clôture en Aluminium</small></h3>
        <p data-i18n="alum.p">Elegant wrought-iron look without the rust. Our aluminum fences are powder-coated for lasting beauty and durability — ideal for front yards across Laval and Montreal.</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="alum.li1">Rust-proof &amp; weatherproof</li>
          <li data-i18n="alum.li2">Classic ornamental styles</li>
          <li data-i18n="alum.li3">Black, bronze &amp; custom colors</li>
          <li data-i18n="alum.li4">Decorative &amp; spear-top options</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link" data-i18n="svc.link">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#128279;</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="chain.h3">Chain-Link Fence<br /><small>Clôture Chaîne</small></h3>
        <p data-i18n="chain.p">Durable and cost-effective chain-link fencing for residential yards, commercial properties and sports areas throughout Greater Montreal and Laval.</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="chain.li1">Galvanized &amp; vinyl-coated</li>
          <li data-i18n="chain.li2">Residential &amp; commercial grade</li>
          <li data-i18n="chain.li3">Security topping options</li>
          <li data-i18n="chain.li4">Quick installation</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link" data-i18n="svc.link">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">&#128295;</div>
        <h3 data-i18n="repair.h3">Fence Repair<br /><small>Réparation de Clôture</small></h3>
        <p data-i18n="repair.p">Storm damage, rot, or sagging panels? We repair all fence types quickly and professionally. Serving all of Montreal, Laval and surrounding cities for prompt fence repairs.</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-i18n="repair.li1">Post replacement</li>
          <li data-i18n="repair.li2">Panel &amp; board replacement</li>
          <li data-i18n="repair.li3">Gate adjustment &amp; repair</li>
          <li data-i18n="repair.li4">Emergency repairs available</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link" data-i18n="svc.link">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
